{"tid":755548,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再有現代導師涉用電話收發DSE保密資料　廉署起訴Kris Lau與其前學生","createTime":"2018-07-25T09:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T11:15:28.000Z","uid":64634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85f8c7d5f6d6b4b37bb614bfa649708f320b9c75","tid":755548,"uid":64634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"廉政公署今日公布，落案起訴43歲現代教育導師劉冠華，以及一名19歲前考評局評卷助理黃子軒。兩人涉嫌貪污及非法取用智能電話，收發2017年香港中學文憑考試（DSE）保密資料。據悉，劉冠華即現代教育英文科導師Kris Lau。<br />\n<br />\n根據廉署公布資料，黃在案發時擔任考評局評卷助理，評閱2017年DSE英國語文科考試答卷。他亦是現代教育前學生，曾修讀劉冠華教授的英文補習班課程。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，黃在無合法權限或合理辯解下收取1000元，透過智能電話，向劉披露當年DSE英國語文科卷三（聆聽及綜合能力）的機密資料。<br />\n<br />\n現代教育導師涉及DSE保密資料已非首次。廉署今年6月起訴四人，涉嫌非法取用智能電話，收發兩屆香港中學文憑考試（DSE）試題。根據廉署公布資料，涉案人士包括現代教育導師蕭志勇和蔡盈盈，即城中著名中文科導師蕭源和蔡怡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180725/s00001/28458f2603de89f1b03d321eec4a745e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180725%2Fs00001%2F28458f2603de89f1b03d321eec4a745e.jpg&h=e3dce42f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明KL 只係播片 都無tip 題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37be93dcb39ae7afee12b6032219c893b91d938d","tid":755548,"uid":188396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"慘啦<br />\n冇kris lau 我中文數學點攞5**<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef561719b25c08928a6ea18c06eecb7ae846109c","tid":7555